collection.name: Valeria Games Genesis Land
collection.description:
The Land of Valeria is an upcoming real time strategy crypto mobile game set to release on iOS and Android. The genesis land consists of  5 elements: fire, water, rock, lightning and grass. To learn more about Valeria Games visit https://www.antebellumgames.com/ or join the discord https://discord.gg/ValeriaGames.
Disclaimer: the VALS token is strictly a utility token and is not considered a security or store of value, 1$VALS Token= 1$VALS Token. $VALS token is currently not available for trade and the token name is subject to change.
